{"id":12113,"date":"2013-02-07T10:46:56","date_gmt":"2013-02-07T15:46:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=12113"},"modified":"2019-05-31T22:40:20","modified_gmt":"2019-05-31T18:40:20","slug":"yawm-al-qiyamah-barefoot","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/07\/yawm-al-qiyamah-barefoot\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Resurrection: People resurrected barefoot, naked, uncircumcised"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>The people will be assembled barefoot, naked, and uncircumcised<\/b>.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, will the men and women look at each other?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>The matter will be too serious for them to notice<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>In another narration, the Prophet recited the verse, &#8220;<strong>As We began creation, so shall We repeat it, a promise binding upon Us. Surely, We will do it.<\/strong>&#8221; (21:104)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6075, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 5107<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e <b>\u062a\u064f\u062d\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064b \u0639\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0629\u06